00:26:17.229 --> 00:26:18.529
How does that feel?

530
00:26:18.578 --> 00:26:20.078
Oh!

531
00:26:21.127 --> 00:26:23.104
Oh. I-I see
what you mean.

532
00:26:23.152 --> 00:26:24.018
They...
[Chuckles]

533
00:26:24.081 --> 00:26:28.057
