pay me for my share.

666
00:34:25.375 --> 00:34:28.169
I believe it comes
to around $8 million.

667
00:34:28.500 --> 00:34:31.203
We both know the firm
doesn't have the money.

668
00:34:32.586 --> 00:34:35.170
You'd rather
tear down hhm than retire?

669
00:34:35.218 --> 00:34:36.586
